channel.title: Category definition for Real-life Bootstrapped Meet-Ups
channel.description: Sometimes it's great to just get out from behind that laptop and *see people*. It's even better when those people are have a level of empathy with your daily challenges. This category is for those bootstrappers who want to arrange meet-ups in their locality.
